Summary: I was taking random pictures and saw what appears to be a UFO in two of them.
divs: sighting detailsi was taking random pictures while on the bus going around landover mall and saw what appears to be a ufo in two of them in the 4:21 pm photos. saucer shaped, kind of a silhouette in front of the sun. could have been a bird, but it doesn't look wingy. clearly not a plane or blimp. possibly a blur of the camera with the sun. but it definitely looks saucer-like. never actually saw it as i was simply holding up my phone\camera snapping pictures. i felt a little wow.
